    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The complexity level of this function is considered low. Scalar functions typically involve straightforward logic and calculations, making them easier to understand and implement compared to more complex function types like multi-statement table-valued functions."
